        <p>Pick one of our three monthly plans and receive unique products from Istanbul's best local shops.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card m-4 col-12 col-lg-3">
        <%= image_tag "https://res.cloudinary.com/drjk0oilg/image/upload/v1587994512/ourhoodimg2_fs6lbr.png", class: "info-card-img w-100 mb-4" %>
        <h4 class='mb-4' style="color: #0DBF6C"><b>Delivered To You</b></h4>
        <p>The most unique Istanbul stores delivered at an address of your preference.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
